description: Gets the list of Microsoft.Compute SKUs available for your Subscription.

subscription_id.description: Subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

value.description: The list of skus available for the subscription.

nextlink.description: The URI to fetch the next page of Resource Skus. Call ListNext() with this URI to fetch the next page of Resource Skus
